     \frac{1}{\sqrt{a}+\sqrt{b}+\sqrt{c}} = \frac{(\sqrt{a}+\sqrt{b}-\sqrt{c})(a+b-c-2\sqrt{ab})}{a^2 + b^2 + c^2 - 2(ab+ac+bc)} 
     \frac{1}{\sqrt{a}+\sqrt{b}+\sqrt{c}} =\frac{\sqrt a+\sqrt b-\sqrt c}{(\sqrt{a}+\sqrt{b}+\sqrt{c})(\sqrt a+\sqrt b-\sqrt c)}=\frac{\sqrt a+\sqrt b-\sqrt c}{(\sqrt a+\sqrt b)^2-(\sqrt c)^2}=\frac{\sqrt a+\sqrt b-\sqrt c}{a+b-c+2\sqrt{ab}}
a+b-c-2\sqrt{ab}
\frac1{\sqrt a+\sqrt b+\sqrt c}=\frac{(\sqrt a+\sqrt b-\sqrt c)(a+b-c-2\sqrt{ab})}{(a+b-c+2\sqrt{ab})(a+b-c-2\sqrt{ab})}
=\frac{(\sqrt a+\sqrt b-\sqrt c)(a+b-c-2\sqrt{ab})}{(a+b-c)^2-(2\sqrt{ab})^2}
=\frac{(\sqrt a+\sqrt b-\sqrt c)(a+b-c-2\sqrt{ab})}{a^2+b^2+c^2+2ab-2bc-2ca-4ab}=...
(\sqrt{a}+\sqrt{b}+\sqrt{c})(\sqrt{a}+\sqrt{b}-\sqrt{c})=(\sqrt{a}+\sqrt{b})^2-c=a+b-c+2\sqrt{ab}
(a+b-c+2\sqrt{ab})(a+b-c-2\sqrt{ab})=(a+b-c)^2-4ab=a^2 + b^2 + c^2 - 2(ab+ac+bc)
